Package wifindus.eye

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DeviceEventListener
    An object which listens for changes in the state of a Device object.
    EyeApplicationListener
    An object which listens for the creation of one of the core Eye platform objects.
    IncidentEventListener
    An object which listens for changes in the state of a Incident object.
    NodeEventListener
    An object which listens for changes in the state of a Node object.
    UserEventListener
    An object which listens for changes in the state of a User object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Atmosphere
    An immutable, serializable packet of data describing the atmospheric condition at an object's location.
    Device
    A client device in use by medical, security or wifindus personnel.
    EyeApplication
    A general base for Eye applications that need to maintain a connection to a MySQL database and respond to changes made to Users, Devices, etc.
    EyeMySQLConnection
    A refined MySQLConnection wrapper containing methods specifically for manipulating the Eye project's database.
    Hash
    A global, static class containing WiFindUs hash ID string manipulation functions.
    Incident
    An security, medical or wifindus incident occurring in the field, as reported by field personnel.
    Location
    An immutable, serializable packet of data describing an object's location.
    Node
    A mesh node device forming part of the WFU client network route.
    User
    A member of medical, security, or WiFindUs personnel.
